aVIn its email response to \u201canti-Muslim\u201d comments by attendees of a lecture at Scripps College last week, the Claremont Colleges\u2019 Muslim Student Association urged students to donate to the Council on American-Islamic Relations (CAIR)\u2014which has faced scrutiny by the federal government for its connections to terrorist groups, such as Hamas.
